  "original_title": "\u0d87\u0db3\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dd2 \u0db1\u0dd2\u0dad\u0dd2\u0dba \u0d89\u0dc0\u0dad\u0dca \u0d9a\u0dbb\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Curfew is lifted",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The police media unit says that the police curfew imposed on 7 police divisions in the Western Province will be lifted today at 8:00 am.",
        "The Inspector General of Police has imposed a curfew on the police divisions of Meegamau, Kelaniya, Nugegoda, Galkissa, Colombo (North, Central and South) from 9.00 pm last night until further notice.",
        "However, various parties, including the Sri Lanka Human Rights Commission and the Sri Lanka Bar Association, expressed their opposition to the imposition of the curfew."
      ],
